{"tid":1373453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又話入黑就散","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:11:40.000Z","uid":130981,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cfad22c21bc538f49ed18d7e22b8a0acff345889","tid":1373453,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:30:40.000Z","msg":"難聽都要講<br />\n屌一早講好入黑就黑社會玩哂<br />\n狗又full gear<br />\n你班友勇武又未去到魚革咁屌打d狗<br />\n好心啦 你準備比人拉<br />\n但冇人想你地比人拉<br />\n唔好白白犧牲<br />\n留低做乜呀你又唔係有目標 除左搏拉有咩做到<br />\n留意返現場後方大把和理非係為左掩護大家唔走<br />\n730係個天仲算光嘅時間<br />\n以我所知730真係其中一條前線向後傳嘅<br />\n好多謝各位勇武嘅兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但希望大家都做到有勇有謀<br />\n場仗可能要打好耐<br />\n韓國 台灣 都係長期抗爭"},{"pid":"79e1bbbe19dd6f396cb2f32657a7b3d28263591c","tid":1373453,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"重申多一次，唔明點解前線要留既請入，前線只會係以下三種情況下徹退。<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/drpmgT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/drpmgT</a>"},{"pid":"b40aefc8fd130a6bc76770afb7bed65d824d5dc3","tid":1373453,"uid":30293,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n咪撚再開分化post<br />\n<br />\n和理 勇武 <br />\n同一陣線 槍口對外<br />\n尊重每個人決定<br />\n<br />\n矛頭指向政府 黑警<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"9bf7c4771628742b4b9b362643253ab45b7c2a0c","tid":1373453,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"勇武決定左要留，已經做好比攻擊準備，<br />\n真正留喺現場嘅勇武兄弟，係唔會怪自已人離開，<br />\n即史離開現場，和理非心中都會支持留守兄弟決定，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留下：支持；離開：專重</span></span><br />\n唔需要班3毛上連登開po分化代言"},{"pid":"0bda45150ab4e0087ceb805a19af15cfce337bb9","tid":1373453,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79e1bbbe19dd6f396cb2f32657a7b3d28263591c","tid":1373453,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"重申多一次，唔明點解前線要留既請入，前線只會係以下三種情況下徹退。<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/drpmgT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/drpmgT</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:34:28.000Z","msg":"現場情況就係渠左邊被推到橋位(過到右邊)而右邊啱啱食左強亂哂 730果下係必須要退 唔退就會比人夾<br />\n再者入黑 黑社會出嚟參戰 好易永久傷殘"},{"pid":"57bf96301e86968a61226fa3a4f1467f21dfa695","tid":1373453,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bf7c4771628742b4b9b362643253ab45b7c2a0c","tid":1373453,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"勇武決定左要留，已經做好比攻擊準備，<br />\n真正留喺現場嘅勇武兄弟，係唔會怪自已人離開，<br />\n即史離開現場，和理非心中都會支持留守兄弟決定，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留下：支持；離開：專重</span></span><br />\n唔需要班3毛上連登開po分化代言"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:36:01.000Z","msg":"拉一個少一個"},{"pid":"f08aaa5fcc6ad58816f6afbed4e7379daa2beeeb","tid":1373453,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e4dbcbba652b1e898bebd4cf9219b210e6ebf7","tid":1373453,"uid":273708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtbFgPG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtbFgPG.png&h=5945330e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日見啦"},{"pid":"57547dc912110b928ab8cc3ac5d643c8724f530f","tid":1373453,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"喂大佬負皮都解釋下好喎"},{"pid":"6589f3829415c4cb00c8f4daaed70ae02f0816a4","tid":1373453,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80e4dbcbba652b1e898bebd4cf9219b210e6ebf7","tid":1373453,"uid":273708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtbFgPG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%